## 🏗️ Project Architecture

```
cinescope/
├── 🎯 app/                         # Next.js App Router
│   ├── 🔐 (auth)/                 # Authentication pages
│   │   ├── signin/                # Sign in page with trailers
│   │   └── signup/                # Registration with validation
│   ├── 🌐 api/                    # API routes
│   │   ├── auth/                  # NextAuth.js endpoints
│   │   ├── movies/                # Movie data & recommendations
│   │   ├── watchlist/             # Watchlist management
│   │   └── onboarding/            # User profiling
│   ├── 📊 dashboard/              # Main application
│   ├── 📝 onboarding/             # AI personality analysis
│   ├── 📋 watchlist/              # Movie tracking
│   ├── ⭐ ratings/                # User reviews & ratings
│   └── 👥 social/                 # Community features
├── 🧩 components/                 # Reusable components
│   ├── YouTubeTrailerBackground   # Cinematic backgrounds
│   └── SessionProvider           # Auth context
├── 🔧 lib/                       # Core utilities
│   ├── smart-ai-recommendation-engine # Custom AI system
│   ├── movie-service             # TMDB integration
│   ├── social-service            # Community features
│   └── notification-service      # Smart alerts
├── 🗄️ prisma/                     # Database schema
└── 📄 types/                      # TypeScript definitions
```

