## 🎯 AI Personality Types

Our custom AI recognizes 6 distinct movie personality types:

| 🧠 **Intellectual Explorer** | 💖 **Emotional Connector** | 🎉 **Entertainment Seeker** |
|----------------------------|---------------------------|---------------------------|
| Complex narratives, thought-provoking themes | Character-driven stories, emotional depth | Blockbusters, crowd-pleasers, fun |

| 🚀 **Escapist Explorer** | 🎭 **Critical Analyst** | 🌟 **Nostalgic Dreamer** |
|------------------------|----------------------|------------------------|
| Fantasy, adventure, otherworldly | Artistic merit, technical excellence | Classic cinema, timeless stories |

